</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h1 id="插入and主键自增" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#插入and主键自增" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 插入and主键自增</h1>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token annotation punctuation">@Test</span>
<span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">insertUser</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token class-name">User</span> user <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">User</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    user<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">setAge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    user<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">setName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"邓腾浩"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    user<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">setEmail</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"mitdth@163.com"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token keyword">int</span> insert <span class="token operator">=</span> userMapper<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">insert</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>user<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>user<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token class-name">System</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>insert<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>插入时默认是可以不用填写id的，id会自动用<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/lq18050010830/article/details/89845790" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">雪花算法<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>生成</p>
<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/0Eumenides/upic/main/2023/04/19/image-20200923195105002.png" alt="image-20200923195105002"></p>
<p>如果需要改为自增则：在实体类主键字段上加上注解<code v-pre>@TableId(type = IdType.AUTO)</code>，注意数据库中的主键一定也是要自增的</p>
